Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org
Reviewed-by: Nicolas Saenz Julienne <nsaenz@amazon.com>
Reviewed-by: David Woodhouse <dwmw@amazon.co.uk>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250826143816.38686-1-eugkoira@amazon.com
